{
  "stem": "1292.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it wasn't so much the hunger as the terrible fear of uncertainty and the terrible fear of being punished or shot for no reason, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was so unpredictable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And-- no, no, that was the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, my God.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I can, myself, recall such a-- I-- I-- I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't good nourishment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But for myself, I managed with soup and whatever I can remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That wasn't-- the hunger is a-- was terrible fear and terrible thing what we did see.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like, there was no crematoriums in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they was bringing transport of people-- Jewish and non-Jewish-- and shooting them to the grave and burning them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the smell of-- you know, up in the air of these bodies was just absolutely unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- I did-- I did see, on one occasion, where the mother did carry-- she had-- did have-- they did strip naked always.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she did go walk with the child in her arm, with a infant, to the grave which was prepared.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a woman's-- woman SS-- SS woman as well as men.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- one was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was watching this for this mother going to the grave with a infant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, what sort of people was that, you know-- and you think?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they was all shot in the neck and fell into the grave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once was a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was shot, but I-- he wasn't fatally shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he pretended to be dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he was like, dazed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after the execution, before they burned them, he was-- did come out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was shot finally by the Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Absolutely a havoc-- moral havoc.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
